# Google OAuth Environment Variables Example
# This file shows the required environment variables for Google OAuth
# Create a .env.local file (git-ignored) and add these variables

# ============================================
# GOOGLE OAUTH CONFIGURATION
# ============================================

# Get these credentials from Google Cloud Console:
# https://console.cloud.google.com/ → APIs & Services → Credentials

SUPABASE_AUTH_EXTERNAL_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID="your-client-id-here.apps.googleusercontent.com"
SUPABASE_AUTH_EXTERNAL_GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET="your-client-secret-here"

# ============================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ============================================
#
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Create or select a project
# 3. Configure OAuth consent screen (APIs & Services → OAuth consent screen)
# 4. Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID (APIs & Services → Credentials)
#    - Application type: Web application
#    - Name: FairPay Local Development
#
# 5. Configure Authorized redirect URIs:
#    - http://localhost:54321/auth/v1/callback
#    - http://127.0.0.1:54321/auth/v1/callback
#
# 6. Configure Authorized JavaScript origins:
#    - http://localhost:3000
#    - http://127.0.0.1:3000
#
# 7. Copy Client ID and Client Secret
# 8. Create .env.local in project root (this file is git-ignored)
# 9. Add the two variables above with your actual values
# 10. Restart Supabase: supabase stop && supabase start
#
# ============================================
# DETAILED GUIDE
# ============================================
#
# See docs/60-Supabase-Local-Google-Login-Setup.md for complete setup guide
# with screenshots, troubleshooting, and security best practices.

# ============================================
# NOTES
# ============================================
#
# - DO NOT commit .env.local to git (it's in .gitignore)
# - Port 54321 is the default Supabase local API port
# - Port 3000 is the default Vite dev server port
# - For production, create separate credentials with production URLs

# ============================================
# PRODUCTION SETUP
# ============================================
#
# ⚠️ QUAN TRỌNG: Local và Production phải dùng OAuth clients KHÁC NHAU!
#
# Local Development:
#   - Redirect URI: http://localhost:54321/auth/v1/callback
#   - Client: "FairPay Local Development"
#   - Environment: .env.local
#
# Production:
#   - Redirect URI: https://[project-ref].supabase.co/auth/v1/callback
#   - Client: "FairPay Production" (tạo mới)
#   - Environment: Vercel/Platform environment variables
#
# Xem hướng dẫn chi tiết:
#   - Quick fix (15 phút): GOOGLE_OAUTH_PRODUCTION_FIX.md
#   - Full guide: docs/93-Production-OAuth-Security-Fix.md
#
# KHÔNG BAO GIỜ:
#   ❌ Dùng chung credentials giữa local và production
#   ❌ Có localhost trong production OAuth client
#   ❌ Commit credentials vào Git
